{"tid":58292,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"覺唔覺香港做廢老好著數","createTime":"2016-12-28T16:45:52.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-29T02:44:05.000Z","uid":61130,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"35d48f97b33000ee48d73714d2fae41b393d83d6","tid":58292,"uid":61130,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-28T16:45:52.000Z","msg":"做廢老，當時出生岩岩香港發展時期 食住個勢上<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n而家香港好多政策都係幫廢老果邊 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n無咩政策真係幫到年輕人<br />\n要尊重長輩 廢老做錯會屌返你轉頭<br />\n醫療比以前好 以前年代廢老好快死<br />\n可以比後生上位 <br />\n而家廢老去到90 100歲已經平常<br />\n姐係佢地可能唔洗點養上一代人（因為早死）<br />\n但你要養埋佢（因為死唔去）<br />\n呢個年代早後生真係好慘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4ea9dbc12d448dc4db370329c7eeff5f19bc3170","tid":58292,"uid":54181,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-28T16:46:35.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"38dc8ba8b07487a50e2925f3a441634ca0b6404f","tid":58292,"uid":54181,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-28T16:47:07.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"a7974e2fb24f748eef00ac4598d01ecb4b59e649","tid":58292,"uid":61130,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-28T16:48:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我覺得其實廢中（40-60歲著數d）</blockquote><br />\n佢地都係同一黨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c1fc535d70ef96b99235620f071040c24f259956","tid":58292,"uid":48796,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-28T16:53:15.000Z","msg":"根本係政策同輿論向五、六十歲班baby boomer傾斜<br />\n目的係壓制後生仔<br />\n1. 後生仔冇得上位, 方便殖民<br />\n2. 等兩代人互相鬥爭, 無力反共, 拉一派打一派, 支共常用技倆"},{"pid":"e13c92c6a9855003140159a885f01bcfd9b338ee","tid":58292,"uid":4493,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-28T17:59:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>根本係政策同輿論向五、六十歲班baby boomer傾斜<br />\n目的係壓制後生仔<br />\n1. 後生仔冇得上位, 方便殖民<br />\n2. 等兩代人互相鬥爭, 無力反共, 拉一派打一派, 支共常用技倆</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n全世